{"tid":2462229,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中共制裁九名英國政客學者 首度針對外國律師行","createTime":"2021-03-26T01:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T01:38:23.000Z","uid":52779,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4f315578bf7c0ea41652a83ff719b7840e2fdd3d","tid":2462229,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:22:22.000Z","msg":"【🇬🇧英國戰線｜中共制裁九名英國政客學者 首度針對外國律師行】<br />\n<br />\n繼早前針對歐洲發動制裁後，中共外交部剛宣布制裁九名英國公民及四個實體，皆因他們針對新疆散佈虛假消息，強調他們在華財產會被凍結、禁止他們及其家人進入中國領土、中國公民及機構禁止與他們做生意。<br />\n<br />\n受制裁對象包括<br />\n．Tom Tugendhat（下議院外交事務專責委員會主席）<br />\n．Iain Duncan Smith（保守黨前黨魁）<br />\n．Neil O&rsquo;Brien（議會中國問題研究小組成員、保守黨下議院議員）<br />\n．David Alton（上議院議員）<br />\n．Tim Loughton（跨黨派國會香港小組成員）<br />\n．Nusrat Ghani（曾要求各大品牌交代棉花供應來源的保守黨下議院議員）<br />\n．Baroness Helena Kennedy（工黨上議院議員）<br />\n．Sir Geoffrey Nice（在維吾族獨立法庭主持種族滅絕案件的英國御用大律師）<br />\n．Joanne Nicola Smith Finley（研究新疆問題學者）<br />\n．中國研究小組<br />\n．保守黨人權委員會<br />\n．維吾爾獨立法庭<br />\n．埃塞克斯園大律師事務所（今年2月就中共新疆暴行是否構成種族滅絕提供法律意見）<br />\n<br />\n若然比較中共兩次制裁，中共今次對英制裁主要集中政客，沒有像對歐制裁一樣針對行政機關，但卻首度針對提供法律的律師樓，這意味中共不但打擊香港司法獨立，連外國法律意見，只要不符合黨的主旋律，都要批鬥制裁一番。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/guardianworld/status/1375243869122560003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fguardianworld%2Fstatus%2F1375243869122560003&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Ghd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=db16aa94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fguardianworld%2Fstatus%2F1375243869122560003&h=7f87570b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/guardianworld/status/1375243869122560003</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/StuartKLau/status/1375224497687703555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStuartKLau%2Fstatus%2F1375224497687703555&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Ghd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=03acce3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStuartKLau%2Fstatus%2F1375224497687703555&h=d4845515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/StuartKLau/status/1375224497687703555</a><br />\n<br />\n👉訂閱Patreon，了解我的思想、工作、生活：<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/nathanlaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fnathanlaw&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Ghd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=2ced2638\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/nathanlaw</a><br />\n👉訂閱「國際戰線頻道」 零時差緊貼最新動態：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKinternationalfront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKinternationalfront&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Ghd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=40ffa3c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKinternationalfront</a>"},{"pid":"990c83a7d8f79d5aa813f81c17a273c5eacf252b","tid":2462229,"uid":204231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef9e6699ae4b5df7567e73844ed01327477bf2e","tid":2462229,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669383fc6f5f8d4804cf17a329ef44a049470f5f","tid":2462229,"uid":225117,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持最驚你縮"},{"pid":"44c7e3002b09882398561e37360da3fa700344de","tid":2462229,"uid":367595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i